<!-- About Content -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h2 class="font-serif mb-4" style="font-size: 2.5rem;">Our Story</h2>
                <p class="lead mb-4">Since 1985, Luxury Hotel has been synonymous with exceptional hospitality and unparalleled service in the heart of the city.</p>
                <p>What started as a vision to create the perfect blend of comfort, elegance, and personalized service has evolved into one of the most prestigious hotels in the region. Our commitment to excellence has earned us numerous awards and, more importantly, the loyalty of guests from around the world.</p>
                <p>Every detail of your stay is carefully crafted to exceed expectations, from our meticulously designed rooms to our world-class amenities and dedicated staff who anticipate your every need.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/258154/pexels-photo-258154.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&h=400&fit=crop" 
                     alt="Hotel Exterior" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-lg">
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2">
                <h2 class="font-serif mb-4" style="font-size: 2.5rem;">Our Mission</h2>
                <p class="lead mb-4">To provide an extraordinary hospitality experience that creates lasting memories for every guest.</p>
                <p>We believe that true luxury lies in the details â€“ from the thread count of our linens to the temperature of your welcome drink. Our team of hospitality professionals is dedicated to ensuring that every moment of your stay is nothing short of perfect.</p>
                <p>Whether you're here for business or leisure, celebrating a special occasion or simply seeking a peaceful retreat, we're committed to making your experience truly unforgettable.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1">
                <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1134176/pexels-photo-1134176.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&h=400&fit=crop" 
                     alt="Hotel Interior" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-lg">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

